Note: Time and Date is SYSTEM time not GMT. (ie GMT - 6h)




Version 6.4.2



03/07/30 09:40 - Bod

act.comm.c     - Changed colour of tell to #b and yell to #c
constants.c    - Changed Version to 6.4.122
history.c      - Changed colour of tell to #b and yell to #c
ignore.c       - Changed MAX_IGNORE to 100


03/07/03 07:03 - Bod

constants.c    - Changed Version to 6.4.121
fight.c        - Changed so PKOK characters run through normal corpse generation sequence
                 Players flagged KILLER or fights in PKOK rooms still generate empty corpses


12/06/03 09:40 - Bod

act.wizard.c   - Added 3 new imm commands (assigned to IMM_WORLD)
        whereload:  Finds where an object or mobile loads to.  It goes through 
                    the zone commands for each file and shows you all commands 
                    that would load the object or mobile specified and all 
                    relevant information.

        findkey:    Finds the key that goes to the door in the direction 
                    specified, and sends the vnum to the whereload command.

        finddoor:   Finds the door that a key goes to.
constants.c    - Changed Version to 6.4.120
interpreter.c  - Added new imm commands to command_interpreter


11/06/03 17:05 - Bod

casino.c       - More modifications to special(roulette)
config.c       - Tweaked title screen again
constants.c    - Changed Version to 6.4.120c


11/06/03 15:45 - Bod

casino.c       - Made more changes to special(roulette)
               - Banned the use of emote in the roulette room (just in case)
constants.c    - Changed Version to 6.4.120b
gen_cards.c    - In special(poker) barred the use of ":" (emote)


