                 (this happens prior to advance to level 1 so they get max gain)
boards.c       - Added entry for obj 899 (Chalumeau Board)
casino.c       - Changed roulette to take a bit longer (per cycle) and changed
                 bet amounts to 100 - 100000 instead of 1000 to 10mil
