act.wizard.c   - LEVEL_ADMIN can go to PRIVATE rooms (with 2 or more ppl in)
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can use transfer ALL
                 LEVEL_ADMIN+ now sees who is set PLR_LOG
                 Also fixed speacing issue with LOG displaying on PLR:
                 Changed SHUTDOWN so anyone with shutdown command can use 
                 all options (means Britomartis can shutdown die if needed)
                 LEVEL_ADMIN restore on an IMM will now give skills / maxstats
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can set another IMMs invis level
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can toggle another IMMs NOHASSLE flag
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can set a players clan level without IMM_CLAN flag
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can change an online players name  
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can use set <player> goldlevel <value>
                 Xlag now syslogs to LEVEL_ADMIN on BRIEF
                 Removed fubar from immortal_interp
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can immset IMM_ALL and any other flags on same or
                 lower level IMMs (inc self but NOT LEVEL_IMPL IMMs)
                 Immset now syslogs to LEVEL_ADMIN on NORMAL
                 Changed force so force <imm> shutdown is blocked and syslogged
boards.c       - Messages from LEVEL_ADMIN default to colour bright red
                 LEVEL_ADMIN can remove / amend etc any board message
comm.c         - Mud Efficiency now syslogs to LEVEL_ADMIN on COMPLETE
