21/01/03 15:35 - Drusian

act.obj1.c     - Added check to see if player is standing in their own clan donation room
               - ACMD(do_put) : only clan members can put an item in their own donation room
               - Fixed so only clan members of that clan can take an item from their donation room
               - ACMD(do_drop) : only clan members can donate equipment, sacrifice equipment,
                 or drop an item in their clan donation room.
               - Commented out portion to prevented DONATED items from appearing in clan donation
                 rooms. All successful donations will go to Midgaard Donation Room. 
                 
19/01/03 18:55 - Drusian

act.comm.c     - Added #include "ignore.h"
               - Added command to make sure a tell does not get sent to the ignoring party
               - ACMD(do_whisper): removes whisper from ignoring party, still show in history
               - ACMD(do_ask) : removes message, still displays player asking question
               - ACMD(do_qcomm): added check for ignore (and writing?)
               - ACMD(do_gen_com) : added ignore check to do_write
               - ACMD(do_gsay) : added ignore check to do_write
               - ACMD(do_say): sends message to each character vs sending to room
act.offensive.c - Added #include "ignore.h" 
               - Created ACMD(do_ignore)
                 To a maximum list of 50, mortals can ignore mortals. Players cannot ignore 
                 themselves or immortals. Immortals cannot ignore mortals.  A player does not
                 know they are being ignored. Messages to ignored players do not reach the 
                 ignored party but will show up on the sender's screen and in their history.
act.other.c    - Created command to write to ignorelist in pfile.
               - ACMD(do_save) : added command to write to ignorefile if player uses ignore.
act.social.c   - Added #include "ignore.h"
	       - ACMD(do_clantell) : added ignore check to do_write
constants.c    - Added constant "SIGNO" for save ignore
db.c           - Added free ignore list
ignore.c       - Created for IGNORE command - Functions for ignoring players
ignore.h       - Created for IGNORE command- Types for ignore.c
interpreter.c  - Added #include "ignore.h"
               - Added ACMD(do_ignore)
               - Added command ignore to command_interpreter
Makefile.in    - Added to OBJFILES ignore.o
               - Added ignore.o:ignore.c
               - Added ignore.h to act.comm.o, act.offensive.o, act.other.o, act.social.o
                 intepreter.o
objsave.c      - Added case IGNORE_FILE
objsave.h      - Added #define IGNORE_FILE
structs.h      - Added #define PLR_SAVEIGN (Saves the ignore list)
               - Added new structure for ignore list

lib/           - created directory structure for plrignore/               

