                 members including the leader when grouped
               - ACMD(do_quit): fixed to prevent a player from quitting the game with over 100 items
magic.c        - Added new array for failure or controlling of pets. 
               - Check is done when mobs are obtained by charmed person or instant slayer/wolf. If
                 a player exceeds the max follows, excess mobs obtained by aformentioned spells will
                 attack player and their followers. Is not affected by store bought pets. 
                 (Suggested by Goozer)
                 
18/01/03 21:45 - Drusian

boards.c       - Added flags to messages. Flags are stored after the heading after the
                 string so do NOT modify heading_len unless you know what you are doing.
                 MSG_EDITED,MSG_LOCKED are available flags to date.
               - Added flag BOARD_LOCKED. It will not save on crash but could prove to be
                 useful. Flag can only be set by LEVEL_ADMIN+. When flag in place, no
                 edit, writing or removal of messages is possible.
               - Added EDIT message command for boards . Edit works so that LEVEL_IMPL
                 can edit any message. REMOVE_LVL on clanboard will allow for editing of all
                 messages. Messages can be edited by self. 
               - Added LOCK message command for boards. Lock allows you to lock a message 
                 from being removed or edited until unlocked. For general boards, LEVEL_ADMIN
                 can use and for clanboards REMOVE_LVL. Lock board will add the BOARD_LOCKED
                 flag to the board.
               - Added UNLOCK message command for boards. Reverse effect of LOCK. Unlock board
                 will remove the BOARD_LOCKED flag from the board.
               - Added Board_amend_msg(), Board_lock_msg(), Board_unlock_msg(), set_msg_flag(), 
                 unlock_msg(), lock_board(), unlock_board(),msg_locked().
boards.h       - Added msg flags, MSG_EDITED, MSG_LOCKED, MSG_STICKY. MSG_STICKY is not
                 implemented yet.
               - Added board flag : BOARD_LOCKED
               - Added struct message_flag, set_msg_flag(), unlock_msg(),Board_display_msg(),
                 Board_amend_msg(), Board_lock_msg() uses it.
interpreter.c  - Added edit command for interpreter_command
limits.c       - Fixed to display CAPPED value lost on flee vs CALCULATED value lost



