11/12/02 18:00 - Bod

util/
showplay.c     - Added load_room to output info as requested by Mokky
                 Also tidied display and ensurd fixed length for data


11/12/02 17:15 - Bod

act.comm.c     - Changed mute so muted players can see channel history but still not 
                 use channels - requested by Dismal
act.informative.c - Added [-k clanvnum] to display on who -? as suggested by Euximus
act.offensive.c - Fixed do_kick so a failed kick no longer sends miss message and then
                 performs a succesful kick - Found by Drusian
act.wizard.c   - In do_config fixed max_bank_gold xxM display to show properly
                 - reported by Mokky
                 In view_immortals and view_questors fixed Switched: displaying imm's
                 name instead of the mob they are switched into
utils.h        - Changed WAIT_STATE from = (cycle) to
                 #define WAIT_STATE(ch, cycle) { \
                    if ((ch)->desc) (ch)->desc->wait += (cycle); \
                    else if (IS_NPC(ch)) GET_MOB_WAIT(ch) += (cycle); }
                 suggested by Drusian
                 Fixes issue of circling (getting a wait state of 2) being bashed by a
                 mob like elite guards (in same round) and having wait state set to 1
                 and then being able to circle in 1 round stime instead of 2.
                 This way it just increments the wait state so a player being multi 
                 bashed by a group of mobs may not be able to action any commands until
                 they auto flee and likewise its possible for a group of players spam
                 bashing a mob to keep that mob sitting down (this is harder to do than
                 the mobs keep a player from using skills / spells - mob wait state works
                 in attacks whereas players work in combat rounds)


