19/11/02 17:05 - Bod

fight.c          - Discussed with Mokky not enough hp on berzerk now sets player to
                   -3 hp and POS_INCAP - requires first aid or heal to live otherwise
                   will die in about 4 ticks


19/11/02 16:30 - Bod

fight.c          - Made Berzerk harsher! Gained HP / Move will ALWAYS be removed!
                 If this would take the players move below 0 it is set to 0 instead
                 If this would take the players hp below 0 it is instead set to 0 and
                 their position set to STUNNED (tick update will restore hitpoints and
                 put them back to POS_STANDING or heal)
                 If a player ends combat BELOW 0 hp then they are left to be healed,
                 first aided or die with tick update(s)
                 - Topic for debate - should having less than the required hp to be 
                 removed at end of combat set player to POS_INCAPACITATED and -3 hp
                 to require intervention from another player to keep them alive and
                 more specifically increase the need for first aid skill?


19/11/02 15:20 - Bod

act.comm.c       - Changed do_gen_comm, do_qcomm and do_pray so that level_can_chat
                 restriction doesn't affect remorts (ie a lvl 1 1st remort can chat!)
act.informative.c - In do_who changed display for idle: %d to count in minutes not ticks
                 (tch->specials.timer * SECS_PER_MUD_HOUR / SECS_PER_REAL_MIN)
                 as found by Titan (now conforms to view and users)
                 Also changed to display after 5 minutes not 5 ticks
