Version 6.3.118


25/04/02 17:55 - Bod

act.informative.c - Modified who -k to accept arguement like users -c does
                    Duplicated code from users so who -k <clan vnum> lists as expected
                    Requested by Mokky


17/04/02 05:55 - Bod

act.informative.c - MOB_BLINDER added to show_char_to_char (mode 1 - look at char)
                    calls function blind_routine which will blind a char
                    result of looking at a mob flagged BLINDER is you will see
                    the extra descrip of the mob and then be blinded (with no msg)
                    routine returns before providing details on health and equip
                    NB This does NOT activate on peeking (need to know if Glob wishes)
                    Spoke to Glob - Blinder routine added to peek - makes peek fail
                    and sends a message of you have been blinded by looking at x (in do_peek)
