                 In do_clan modified case 6 (raise) so clan_level 1 can't be raised to 2
                 In do_clan modified case 7 (demote) so clan_level 2 can't be demoted to 1


06/03/02 14:45 - Bod

act.informative.c - Made changes to autoexits display (case 8 of do_look)
                 If a player is flagged ROOMFLAGS they will be shown additional
                 information. Namely room number exit leads to and door status.
                 Example: [ Exits: n (3005)  e (3015)  s (3025)  w (3013)  ]


