act.wizard.c   - Modified do_wiznet to display switched imms on wiznet with
                 (Switched: <name of mob switched into>) does not display this
                 to the switched imm. wiznet @ now fully supports display of 
                 switched imms in online / offline and inherits their prefs.
                 Note if a switched imm is writing or mailing they will display
                 as writing / writing mail as opposed to switched.
                 

